source_objects.title: Database Design & Development
source_objects.description: Become a database expert with these courses ranging from basic SQL to Hadoop and Oracle mastery.

items.title: Database Design untuk Pemula
items.headline: Database System Development Lifecycle Stages, Fact Finding Techniques, Database Design Methodologies
objectives_summary: Pelajar memahami cara mendesain database, seperti Database System Development Life Cycle, Fact Finding Techniques, Methodology (Conceptual Database Design, Logical Database Design for The Relational Model, Physical Database for Relational Databases
Pelajar akan tahu lebih banyak tentang Desain database, dan tahu bagaimana menerapkan Desain database dalam proses bisnis.

items.title: SQL e MySQL fundamental - Aprenda tudo sobre CRUD e JOINs

Memahami konsep dan terminologi dalam sistem database, seperti database environment, relational model, normalization technique, ER modeling, danStructured Query Language (SQL)
Membuat dan memodifikasi sebuah tabel dengan pendekatan kebutuhan dari organisasi

items.title: System Design based on Business Processes (Indonesian Ver.)

Understand vision, mission, objectives, strategic business, business functions, business processes, and business activity to drive the design of information system that support business
Understand differences between structured and object approaches in information system design
